In[14]:
folder_path = "/kaggle/input/animal-image-dataset-90-different-animals"

def Get_Data(folder_path):
    data = {"image_path":[], "image_name": []}
    for i in os.listdir(folder_path):
        if os.path.isdir(os.path.join(folder_path, i)):
            folder_1 = os.path.join(folder_path, i)
            for i in os.listdir(folder_1):
                folder_2 = os.path.join(folder_1, i)
                for image_name in os.listdir(folder_2):
                    folder_3 = os.path.join(folder_2, image_name)
                    for image_jpg in os.listdir(folder_3):
                        image_link = os.path.join(folder_3, image_jpg)
                        data["image_path"].append(image_link)
                        data["image_name"].append(image_name)
    return pd.DataFrame(data)

X = df.drop("image_name", axis=1)

In[20]:
x_train, x_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(X, y, test_size=0.1, stratify=y, random_state=42)

for i in [x_train, x_test, y_train, y_test]:
    i.reset_index(drop=True, inplace=True)

                                                x_col=train_df.columns[0],

Fine Tuning Model

In[31]:
model_2.trainable = True
for layers in model_2.layers[:]:
    if isinstance(layers, keras.layers.BatchNormalization):
        layers.trainable = False
        
data_augumentation = keras.Sequential([
    keras.layers.RandomFlip(),
    keras.layers.RandomZoom(height_factor=(0.01, 0.01), width_factor=(0.01, 0.01)),
    keras.layers.RandomRotation(factor=0.2)
], name="augmentation_layer")

model_input = keras.Input(shape=train_generator_2.image_shape)
prep_data = data_augumentation(model_input)
pretrained_model = model_2(prep_data)
x = keras.layers.Flatten()(pretrained_model)
x = keras.layers.Dense(units=512, activation="relu")(x)
x = keras.layers.Dropout(rate=0.5)(x)
x = keras.layers.BatchNormalization()(x)
model_output = keras.layers.Dense(units=90, activation="softmax")(x)
MODEL_2 = keras.Model(inputs=model_input, outputs=model_output)

MODEL_2.summary()
